# D{{N}} — Big-Picture Event Ribbon

**Audience:** Mixed (event names exact, phase headers plain-language).
**When to look at this:** When you need the chronological shape of what happens in the system, with pivotal events highlighted as natural splitters.
**Prose gap closed:** `2-event-storm.md` lists events in tables; this diagram shows the temporal flow on one ribbon with pivotal events tape-marked.

