### What this diagram deliberately does *not* show

- **Hotspots** — see `2-event-storm.md` § Hotspots for unresolved
  questions and conflicts captured during the storm.
- **Commands and policies** — Big-Picture Event Storming intentionally
  stops at events. Commands belong to Process-Level or Software-Design
  level storming (out of v1 scope).
- **Per-event sequence detail** — see Golden-path Sequence diagrams if
  Tier-3 was generated, one per pivotal-event chain.

